%% Circuit breaker state machine - one breaker, many trigger codes
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Armed: engine start

    Armed --> Cooldown: minor breach<br/>stale_tick, wide_spread, stale_market_data
    Cooldown --> Armed: cooldown elapsed

    Armed --> Latched: major breach<br/>max_drawdown, reconcile_mismatch, operator_halt
    Latched --> Armed: operator rearm

    state Armed {
        [*] --> EntriesAllowed
        EntriesAllowed --> EntriesAllowed: pre-trade checks pass
    }


    note right of Armed
        PreTradeValidator checks
        breaker state before entries.
    end note

    note right of Latched
        Reduce-only exits remain allowed
        so flattening can still reach the venue.
    end note
